         <abstract id="aspace_2adefafdd9ec44a385fd135bbad075e3">The collection includes correspondence and other manuscript material concerning the management of deer parks at Newburgh Priory, Yorkshire; Cassiobury Park, Hertfordshire; and Paultons, Hampshire.</abstract>
