      <scopecontent id="aspace_ae70315d300ec8f156baa039b0400514">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection includes correspondence and other manuscript material concerning the management of deer parks at Newburgh Priory, Yorkshire; Cassiobury Park, Hertfordshire; and Paultons, Hampshire. The letters are written to and from various members of the Bainbridge family who provided a succession of park keepers for the three residences.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
